Create The Top Right Visual Map 13

1. Copy and paste the bottom right chart 

2. Move the duplicate chart to the top right

3. Select the Field button, then, delete the threat level on the shared axis

4. Drag and drop the StateName from the fatal police shooting table to the Location Box

5. Click on Insert, then select Image to download the Map Legend from the downloaded Zip file.


Follow the Gif for detailed guidance to format the Map



Click on the link  for information on how to import a shape map into power bi desktop

https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/power-bi/visuals/desktop-shape-map#:~:text=To%20enable%20Shape%20Map%2C%20select,icon%20from%20the%20Visualizations%20pane.
